                    <h3>Icons in circles - sizes</h3>
                    <p>To create an icon in a circle, add a wrapping element to the <code>.icon</code> with the class of <code>.circle-icon</code></p>
                    <p>The alternative sizes available can be applied using the modifying classes <code>.circle-icon--sm</code>, <code>.circle-icon--sm-resp</code>, <code>.circle-icon--lg</code>, <code>.circle-icon--lg-resp</code> ('resp' meaning it has a different size on mobile and desktop)</p>
                    <p>There is also a mixin available to customise the circle icon size <a href="sass-tools.html#toolsIconsInCircles">here</a></p>

{{> snippet-icon-circle-sizes }}

